00:59:47,783 --> 00:59:49,423
- Then... - But...

815
00:59:50,693 --> 00:59:53,493
I had never imagined us living a life together.

816
00:59:57,294 --> 00:59:58,434
Are you disappointed?

817
01:00:00,133 --> 01:00:01,234
Quite deeply.

818
01:00:03,934 --> 01:00:05,742
Can't you start giving it some thought starting today?

819
01:00:05,743 --> 01:00:07,004
I can't do that...

820
01:00:10,544 --> 01:00:12,513
because my future seems way too bleak.

821
01:00:15,013 --> 01:00:16,683
We can get the students back.

822
01:00:16,684 --> 01:00:17,984
It's not about that.

823
01:00:20,783 --> 01:00:21,894
The academy...

824
01:00:27,593 --> 01:00:29,294
I think I can quit.

825
01:00:33,734 --> 01:00:35,374
The year you got accepted into the university,

826
01:00:35,633 --> 01:00:37,803
Mr. Kim bought me a used car.

827
01:00:39,803 --> 01:00:40,803
I remember that.

828
01:00:41,243 --> 01:00:43,173
You got the car before you could get your license.

829
01:00:45,544 --> 01:00:47,243
That was enough to make me feel proud.

830
01:00:48,584 --> 01:00:51,354
I was clearly the poorest one among my friends.

831
01:00:51,723 --> 01:00:53,184
But it felt like my status had changed.

832
01:00:54,854 --> 01:00:56,593
I was over the moon, so I worked really hard.

833
01:00:57,993 --> 01:00:59,963
Later on, I forgot what for I was making money.

834
01:00:59,964 --> 01:01:01,564
Chasing the money became my goal.

835
01:01:03,593 --> 01:01:05,464
I started this job to pay the tuition for my studies.

836
01:01:05,533 --> 01:01:07,433
But I barely spent time on my own studies.

837
01:01:07,434 --> 01:01:08,734
I only managed to pass my classes.

838
01:01:11,673 --> 01:01:12,774
But...

839
01:01:14,274 --> 01:01:16,073
after losing almost all of my students,

840
01:01:16,544 --> 01:01:17,644
I was reminded again...

841
01:01:19,343 --> 01:01:21,454
why I wanted to earn money.

842
01:01:23,783 --> 01:01:24,823
Funny. Isn't it?

843
01:01:26,254 --> 01:01:27,254
Not at all.

844
01:01:29,024 --> 01:01:31,763
You told me that everything I built crumbled away because of me.

845
01:01:32,863 --> 01:01:35,863
But you were wrong. I don't think that's true.

846
01:01:40,464 --> 01:01:42,504
It's the contrary. Should I say...

847
01:01:42,704 --> 01:01:45,303
the fog that was covering my eyes for a long time finally lifted?

848
01:01:49,573 --> 01:01:51,044
Then I saw it.

849
01:01:53,414 --> 01:01:55,714
I saw the long-overdue studies I had been putting off.

850
01:02:01,084 --> 01:02:02,754
I can't guarantee any results.

851
01:02:04,254 --> 01:02:06,363
I don't know how long it will take for me to finish.

852
01:02:06,794 --> 01:02:09,734
But if I were to achieve something then,

853
01:02:10,693 --> 01:02:12,234
you could give it to me then.

854
01:02:14,164 --> 01:02:15,234
My well-deserved diploma.

855
01:02:23,343 --> 01:02:24,843
I'll give you everything you want.

856
01:02:26,644 --> 01:02:27,684
Thank you.

857
01:02:29,814 --> 01:02:32,283
But whatever you decide to do,

858
01:02:33,323 --> 01:02:34,894
let me support you.

859
01:02:40,964 --> 01:02:42,164
I'll wait for your answer.

860
01:02:46,263 --> 01:02:47,303
How sweet.

861
01:02:52,073 --> 01:02:53,803
I'm going to work.

862
01:02:54,874 --> 01:02:56,113
Mom, wait!

863
01:02:56,714 --> 01:02:59,184
What? What is it?

864
01:02:59,984 --> 01:03:01,144
Mom, hold on.

865
01:03:01,854 --> 01:03:03,153
Could you sit there for a moment?

866
01:03:03,383 --> 01:03:05,323
What? Do you need money?

867
01:03:05,653 --> 01:03:06,854
Sit down.

868
01:03:09,153 --> 01:03:10,223
What is it?

869
01:03:15,294 --> 01:03:16,533
Mom, help me get married.

870
01:03:19,434 --> 01:03:20,464
I must get married.

871
01:03:22,234 --> 01:03:23,303
Do you have a girlfriend?

872
01:03:24,004 --> 01:03:25,943
Why would I ask if I didn't?

873
01:03:28,144 --> 01:03:29,513
What does she do?

874
01:03:29,644 --> 01:03:31,274
How old is she? How long have you been dating her?

875
01:03:33,314 --> 01:03:34,343
It's Ms. Nam Cheong Mi.

876
01:03:37,883 --> 01:03:40,124
Here's what a lot of my married friends told me.

877
01:03:41,153 --> 01:03:42,223
When I meet the one I'm destined to marry,

878
01:03:42,693 --> 01:03:44,354
I'll know it the moment I meet her.

879
01:03:47,894 --> 01:03:50,593
I think I will end up becoming her husband.

880
01:03:54,204 --> 01:03:55,874
You bought an apartment in Pyeongchon, right?

881
01:03:57,274 --> 01:03:58,343
Can I have that?

882
01:03:59,104 --> 01:04:00,943
And help us open up an academy in that neighbourhood.

883
01:04:01,573 --> 01:04:02,613
I want that to be my wedding gift.

884
01:04:06,584 --> 01:04:07,644
Gosh.

885
01:04:09,084 --> 01:04:10,084
What?

886
01:04:38,283 --> 01:04:39,644
You're here early.

887
01:04:45,454 --> 01:04:46,484
Hey.

888
01:04:48,354 --> 01:04:50,024
You seem quite absorbed in it. What is it?

889
01:04:50,254 --> 01:04:51,524
You didn't even notice me coming in.

890
01:04:53,823 --> 01:04:55,164
I was watching lecture videos of the top-tier instructors.

891
01:04:59,464 --> 01:05:01,834
I also watch yours and Mr. Lee's lecture videos.

892
01:05:03,073 --> 01:05:04,073
Mine?

893
01:05:05,973 --> 01:05:07,274
I'm quite motivated...

894
01:05:07,903 --> 01:05:09,414
because my colleagues are so talented.

895
01:05:15,053 --> 01:05:17,414
Do you come in this early every day? I didn't know.

896
01:05:18,254 --> 01:05:20,954
I do. I'm an ambitious type.

897
01:05:23,124 --> 01:05:24,124
I'll let you finish.

898
01:05:27,664 --> 01:05:29,032
- Good morning. - Hello.

899
01:05:29,033 --> 01:05:30,164
- Hello. - Hello.

900
01:05:32,033 --> 01:05:33,863
- You're here early. - Of course.

901
01:05:38,073 --> 01:05:39,403
Let's see.

902
01:05:49,113 --> 01:05:50,184
My son.

903
01:05:51,153 --> 01:05:53,484
Don't goof around. I need you to be serious right now.

904
01:05:54,684 --> 01:05:56,323
I told you everything.

905
01:05:56,993 --> 01:05:59,164
How could I be more serious than this?

906
01:06:00,923 --> 01:06:01,964
Gosh.

907
01:06:04,064 --> 01:06:06,504
"What's the use of your studies?"

908
01:06:07,263 --> 01:06:08,673
"When will you become a professor?"

909
01:06:09,434 --> 01:06:11,573
She was the only one who never asked me these things.

910
01:06:14,743 --> 01:06:15,943
She gives me...

911
01:06:16,673 --> 01:06:18,214
a strong sense of certainty.

912
01:06:20,414 --> 01:06:23,113
Does she like you back?

913
01:06:23,454 --> 01:06:24,454
Really?

914
01:06:26,423 --> 01:06:28,184
Are you more concerned about her feelings than mine?

915
01:06:30,053 --> 01:06:32,164
Are you sure she's into you?

916
01:06:35,734 --> 01:06:36,993
Open an academy in Pyeongchon.

917
01:06:38,164 --> 01:06:40,004
With that, I'll be able to make sure she's completely into me.

918
01:06:40,903 --> 01:06:41,934
Do you think I'm crazy?

919
01:06:44,673 --> 01:06:46,274
Why go that far?

920
01:06:47,544 --> 01:06:49,374
If she wants to make it as an instructor, it should be here.

921
01:06:51,343 --> 01:06:52,383
What?

922
01:06:58,153 --> 01:07:01,153
(Vice-director's Office)

923
01:07:26,684 --> 01:07:29,584
(Daechi Chase)

924
01:07:50,434 --> 01:07:52,374
Why are you looking at me like that?

925
01:07:53,403 --> 01:07:55,172
Everyone knew that...

926
01:07:55,173 --> 01:07:58,882
I wanted to open up an academy at one point.

927
01:07:58,883 --> 01:08:00,443
Yes. That's true. But...

928
01:08:01,754 --> 01:08:04,754
Wait. So...

929
01:08:05,854 --> 01:08:08,184
Academies and reputations go hand in hand.

930
01:08:08,894 --> 01:08:11,193
Gosh. You've gotten this far with Daechi Chase.

931
01:08:11,254 --> 01:08:14,592
I thought it would be a great waste to let it fade away.

932
01:08:14,593 --> 01:08:17,463
So you're telling me...

933
01:08:17,464 --> 01:08:20,133
Keep paying the instructors.

934
01:08:20,634 --> 01:08:22,474
Money is a great way of showing support.

935
01:08:23,403 --> 01:08:25,874
Besides, we must prepare for the next semester.

936
01:08:26,903 --> 01:08:30,014
You ought to hold a big recruitment event like before.

937
01:08:36,514 --> 01:08:38,554
I'm sure you have demands.

938
01:08:43,594 --> 01:08:44,794
Please tell me.

939
01:08:44,993 --> 01:08:47,224
You can move into the vice-director's office tomorrow.

940
01:08:47,393 --> 01:08:49,593
No. You can even move in there today.

941
01:08:49,594 --> 01:08:51,764
Gosh. No.

942
01:08:53,704 --> 01:08:55,103
Well,

943
01:08:55,603 --> 01:08:56,874
since you asked,

944
01:08:58,474 --> 01:09:00,943
- I do have one condition. - Please.

945
01:09:02,643 --> 01:09:04,474
I want you to support...

946
01:09:05,483 --> 01:09:09,554
Ms. Nam as the new face of the academy.

947
01:09:13,353 --> 01:09:17,094
Having Ms. Seo...

948
01:09:18,393 --> 01:09:20,794
as the face of our academy...

949
01:09:21,294 --> 01:09:22,664
won't be wise.

950
01:09:23,834 --> 01:09:26,164
Well, yes. I understand your concern.

951
01:09:26,304 --> 01:09:29,203
Ms. Nam is very talented.

952
01:09:29,204 --> 01:09:30,834
She has the potential to become a star instructor too.

953
01:09:31,233 --> 01:09:32,643
She's easy on the eyes too.

954
01:09:34,374 --> 01:09:37,044
She's not lacking in any way. She's indeed smart.

955
01:09:37,143 --> 01:09:38,174
Right.

956
01:09:39,643 --> 01:09:43,183
I understand that you won't be happy with Hye Jin.

957
01:09:43,683 --> 01:09:45,424
But why her of all instructors?

958
01:09:47,153 --> 01:09:49,393
She has what it takes to be an instructor...

959
01:09:49,924 --> 01:09:51,724
who makes one million dollars a year.

960
01:09:53,523 --> 01:09:57,134
I want to help her succeed, so I can give her to my son.

961
01:09:58,193 --> 01:09:59,204
Give my academy to your son?

962
01:10:02,033 --> 01:10:03,374
Gosh, no.

963
01:10:04,773 --> 01:10:06,443
I meant Ms. Nam.

964
01:10:22,893 --> 01:10:23,893
Get me a different one.

965
01:10:24,393 --> 01:10:26,794
No. You drink way too much coffee.

966
01:10:28,294 --> 01:10:31,433
There are other drinks. Why the medicinal herb tea with jujubes?

967
01:10:32,233 --> 01:10:33,334
It makes me look old.

968
01:10:35,233 --> 01:10:38,174
I want you to live a long life.

969
01:10:40,643 --> 01:10:43,113
You don't look old. You look gorgeous.

970
01:10:43,743 --> 01:10:45,844
Just drink it. If you don't like it, I'll get you a different one.

971
01:10:46,983 --> 01:10:48,084
I won't like it.

972
01:10:58,224 --> 01:11:01,124
You said you experienced a lot of new things because of me.

973
01:11:02,094 --> 01:11:04,634
Was it the day we had our first kiss?

974
01:11:09,804 --> 01:11:11,334
I'll have you try out different food...

975
01:11:11,573 --> 01:11:13,743
and take you to places you haven't been to before.

976
01:11:40,464 --> 01:11:42,504
There's an investor who wants...

977
01:11:42,804 --> 01:11:45,474
to help financially until the academy stabilizes again.

978
01:11:49,073 --> 01:11:50,443
It's Ms. Kim Hyo Im.

979
01:11:51,014 --> 01:11:52,183
That's great.

980
01:11:52,683 --> 01:11:53,914
That's great news.

981
01:11:59,724 --> 01:12:01,893
But why don't you look happy?

982
01:12:02,594 --> 01:12:05,094
Well, the thing is,

983
01:12:05,863 --> 01:12:07,224
Ms. Kim...

984
01:12:08,294 --> 01:12:10,134
wants someone else to be the face of the academy.

985
01:12:11,693 --> 01:12:12,903
She raised concern that...

986
01:12:14,004 --> 01:12:16,474
Hye Jin might not be the best person to be the face of our academy.

987
01:12:19,403 --> 01:12:20,474
I'm sorry.

988
01:12:21,174 --> 01:12:23,773
Gosh. It's very difficult for me to turn down her offer.

989
01:12:25,743 --> 01:12:27,283
So Ms. Nam will be the new face.

990
01:12:31,983 --> 01:12:34,054
Gosh, I'm disappointed in Ms. Kim.

991
01:12:36,023 --> 01:12:37,724
Gosh. She's Seoung Gyu's mom.

992
01:12:37,893 --> 01:12:40,523
I think Mr. Lee Myeong Jun will be really disappointed.

993
01:12:42,164 --> 01:12:44,093
A new leader who made a selfless decision for the academy.

994
01:12:44,094 --> 01:12:45,634
He must have had his hopes up.

995
01:12:47,704 --> 01:12:48,833
What are you talking about?

996
01:12:48,834 --> 01:12:50,933
I won't renew his contract.

997
01:12:57,113 --> 01:12:58,174
Gosh.

998
01:12:59,544 --> 01:13:01,643
So what do you think?

999
01:13:07,924 --> 01:13:08,993
I'm bowing out.

1000
01:13:10,023 --> 01:13:11,094
What?

1001
01:13:11,823 --> 01:13:12,863
I'm done.

1002
01:13:19,403 --> 01:13:22,933
(Daechi Chase)

1003
01:13:41,823 --> 01:13:44,493
By the way, isn't there a fancy term for this?

1004
01:13:44,993 --> 01:13:46,323
Buying a position with money?

1005
01:13:49,233 --> 01:13:50,294
You mean "maegwan maegik?"

1006
01:13:50,764 --> 01:13:53,504
Hey, I'm making an investment.

1007
01:13:55,164 --> 01:13:56,933
Gosh. Why are you laughing?

1008
01:13:57,304 --> 01:13:59,474
Do you really think I bought this position with money?

1009
01:13:59,643 --> 01:14:01,304
No. There were students...

1010
01:14:02,014 --> 01:14:04,544
who asked me what kind of magic "maegwan maegik" was.

1011
01:14:07,783 --> 01:14:09,514
- I see. - I see. "Magic."

1012
01:14:11,584 --> 01:14:14,624
I'll even miss those students who asked these ridiculous questions.

1013
01:14:21,363 --> 01:14:24,733
Gosh. I'm so disappointed that you're leaving.

1014
01:14:26,834 --> 01:14:27,933
Hey.

1015
01:14:28,704 --> 01:14:31,334
- Are you done packing? - Yes, I'm almost done.

1016
01:14:32,844 --> 01:14:35,004
Shouldn't we hire a truck or something?

1017
01:14:35,073 --> 01:14:36,613
You worked in this academy for ten years.

1018
01:14:37,643 --> 01:14:39,183
I kept moving a few things whenever I had a chance.

1019
01:14:41,544 --> 01:14:43,113
Please take good care of Min Ji.

1020
01:14:44,153 --> 01:14:46,322
Gosh. I should ask her to take good care of me.

1021
01:14:46,323 --> 01:14:47,523
She's been here longer than me.

1022
01:14:48,454 --> 01:14:52,224
Mr. Lee pled and begged me for four days to snatch her from me.

1023
01:14:52,393 --> 01:14:53,964
Don't forget that I supported you.

1024
01:14:56,134 --> 01:14:57,164
I'll buy you a drink.

1025
01:14:57,794 --> 01:14:59,004
You're free today, right?

1026
01:14:59,264 --> 01:15:01,063
Well, not today. Let's take a rain check.

1027
01:15:01,433 --> 01:15:03,073
I have an important plan today.

1028
01:15:03,903 --> 01:15:04,903
What?

1029
01:15:06,374 --> 01:15:07,443
The last class.

1030
01:15:20,454 --> 01:15:22,454
(Daechi Chase)

1031
01:15:32,863 --> 01:15:35,733
You must train yourself to articulate your thoughts clearly.

1032
01:15:36,903 --> 01:15:39,403
When you can express your thoughts using precise vocabulary...

1033
01:15:40,174 --> 01:15:42,344
and well-constructed sentences,

1034
01:15:42,544 --> 01:15:44,544
interpreting other people's writing becomes easy.

1035
01:15:45,514 --> 01:15:47,182
If you just focus on mindlessly solving questions...

1036
01:15:47,183 --> 01:15:48,283
from study books without this training,

1037
01:15:48,813 --> 01:15:51,554
it will be the same as leaving your grades up to luck.

1038
01:15:52,653 --> 01:15:55,023
Once in a blue moon, there may be a lucky day...

1039
01:15:55,823 --> 01:15:58,424
when you do really well on the exam because you're in the zone.

1040
01:15:59,323 --> 01:16:00,593
But what would happen...

1041
01:16:00,594 --> 01:16:02,664
if you were to fool yourself into believing that's your true grade?

1042
01:16:04,634 --> 01:16:05,664
Yes.

1043
01:16:06,233 --> 01:16:07,532
You'll cry when you get the results...

1044
01:16:07,533 --> 01:16:09,403
of the college entrance exam and end up on the news.

1045
01:16:11,773 --> 01:16:12,903
Embark on the right path.

1046
01:16:13,943 --> 01:16:16,544
Seek precise vocabulary, sentences, and expressions.

1047
01:16:17,174 --> 01:16:19,384
When you have them, your grades will be unchanging.

1048
01:16:19,943 --> 01:16:23,153
Your studies today will be your asset for the rest of your life.

1049
01:16:24,254 --> 01:16:25,853
- Understood? - Yes.

1050
01:16:26,783 --> 01:16:27,783
Any questions?

1051
01:16:30,523 --> 01:16:32,054
Refer to me as an instructor too.

1052
01:16:34,363 --> 01:16:35,393
Sir.

1053
01:16:37,363 --> 01:16:38,834
Tell us about your first love.

1054
01:16:39,103 --> 01:16:40,164
Gosh.

1055
01:16:41,704 --> 01:16:43,134
- Hey, Seo Hye Jin. - Yes.

1056
01:16:43,273 --> 01:16:46,103
Sometimes, you use an advanced technique on me.

1057
01:16:48,174 --> 01:16:50,643
Sir. Are you married?

1058
01:16:52,643 --> 01:16:53,643
Not yet.

1059
01:16:54,384 --> 01:16:56,483
I already proposed to her. I'm begging her to take me.

1060
01:16:57,283 --> 01:16:58,313
Sir.

1061
01:16:58,813 --> 01:17:00,823
- Good luck. - Come on.

1062
01:17:02,153 --> 01:17:03,624
Since we're on the subject, let me ask you this.

1063
01:17:04,323 --> 01:17:05,964
- Since you're a girl. Yes. - I am?

1064
01:17:08,464 --> 01:17:10,233
- An apartment in Gangnam... - Okay.

1065
01:17:10,563 --> 01:17:12,704
Do I need stuff like that to get her to say yes?

1066
01:17:12,933 --> 01:17:14,033
Probably not.

1067
01:17:14,164 --> 01:17:16,133
Then should I float up balloons at a hotel...

1068
01:17:16,134 --> 01:17:17,334
and prepare an expensive designer bag?

1069
01:17:17,733 --> 01:17:19,374
Should I throw her an event like that?

1070
01:17:20,974 --> 01:17:22,174
Probably not.

1071
01:17:59,584 --> 01:18:00,613
Then how about this?

1072
01:18:01,914 --> 01:18:03,613
I bought it a while ago. I've been carrying for a while.

1073
01:18:04,683 --> 01:18:05,954
My girlfriend...

1074
01:18:06,054 --> 01:18:08,424
might start going to school where there are a lot of guys.

1075
01:18:09,124 --> 01:18:10,293
"She's taken."

1076
01:18:10,294 --> 01:18:11,823
